videos.headline: Jake Herslow adjusts his route, reels in 49-yard TD pass
videos.description: Clayton Tune has all the time in the world to find Jake Herslow in the open field as Houston extends its lead over UConn.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jake Herslow adjusts his route, reels in 49-yard TD pass) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: UConn's Kevens Clercius makes amazing diving catch for a TD
videos.description: Kevens Clercius goes full extension to grab a 34-yard touchdown pass from Steven Krajewski and get UConn on the board.
